---
// biome-ignore lint/correctness/noUnusedImports: Biome bug
import RootLayout from "../../layouts/RootLayout.astro";
---

<RootLayout title="Resume">

  <main
    class="w-full mx-auto max-w-5xl py-12 px-8 sm:px-12 space-y-8 print:py-0 print:px-0 print:space-y-4 print:text-[11pt] text-gray-900">

    <header class="space-y-6 print:space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-4xl print:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Chris Lambe</h1>
      <hr class="border-gray-300 print:my-2">
      <ul class="grid print:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-sm md:text-base print:text-[10pt]">
        <li>Portland, ME</li>
        <li class="work-it">moc.ebmalsirhc@olleh</li>
        <li><a target="_blank" href="tel:+15127881216">(512) 788-1216</a></li>
        <li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chrislambe/">linkedin.com/in/chrislambe</a></li>
        <li><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/chrislambe">github.com/chrislambe</a></li>
        <li><a target="_blank" href="https://chrislambe.com/">chrislambe.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </header>

    <p class="leading-relaxed print:leading-normal">
      Principal-level software engineer with ~20 years of individual contributor experience in fast-paced startup
      environments. Most recently served as CTO of Splashmetrics, an AI-driven B2B marketing platform, staying highly
      hands-on building features with TypeScript, React, and PostgreSQL. Daily user of AI-assisted development tools and
      active builder of LLM-powered product features. Earlier in my career, spent 3+ years building patient-provider
      communication software, navigating HIPAA and the realities of healthcare app development. Advocate for
      domain-driven design, working with subject matter experts to chip away at uncertainty and model software around
      the real-world problems it solves. Deeply curious and eager to dive into systems to solve problems, with a strong
      enthusiasm for learning and acquiring new skills.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-gray-300 print:my-2">

    <section class="space-y-4 print:space-y-2">
      <h2 class="text-2xl print:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Core Skills</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 print:grid-cols-3 gap-6 print:gap-4">
        <div class="space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg print:text-base pb-1">Architecture & AI</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 print:space-y-0">
            <li>Domain-Driven Design (DDD)</li>
            <li>Clean/Hexagonal Architecture</li>
            <li>LLM Integration</li>
            <li>AI-Assisted Development</li>
            <li>Distributed System Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg print:text-base pb-1">Languages & Libraries</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 print:space-y-0">
            <li>TypeScript</li>
            <li>React</li>
            <li>NextJS, TanStack Start</li>
            <li>GraphQL</li>
            <li>Effect (TypeScript library)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg print:text-base pb-1">Infrastructure & Data</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 print:space-y-0">
            <li>Cloudflare / AWS</li>
            <li>PostgreSQL</li>
            <li>Terraform</li>
            <li>Docker</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-300 print:my-2">

    <section class="space-y-6 print:space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl print:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Professional Experience</h2>

      <div class="space-y-8 print:space-y-4">

        <div class="job-block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl print:text-lg font-bold">Chief Technology Officer</h3>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 whitespace-nowrap">April 2023 - Present</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-lg print:text-base italic text-gray-700 mb-2 print:mb-1">Splashmetrics</div>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
            <li>
              Steered overall technical direction and architecture for an AI-driven B2B marketing platform while
              remaining highly hands-on as an individual contributor across the stack.
            </li>
            <li>
              Applied Domain-Driven Design (DDD) principles to build stable, scalable software systems.
            </li>
            <li>
              Integrated LLMs into the core product to automate buyer journey planning and content creation, directly
              tying AI capabilities to business value.
            </li>
            <li>
              Drove engineering efficiency by deeply integrating AI development tools into daily workflows,
              significantly increasing personal and team leverage.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="job-block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl print:text-lg font-bold">Software Architect</h3>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 whitespace-nowrap">July 2019 - April 2023</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-lg print:text-base italic text-gray-700 mb-2 print:mb-1">SevenPico</div>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
            <li>
              Architected and engineered a large-scale distributed microservices system powering automated coffee-making
              robots for Briggo (subsequently acquired by Costa Coffee).
            </li>
            <li>
              Designed and implemented a robust API layer via <strong>GraphQL</strong>, orchestrating complex state
              management between physical hardware sensors, order queues, and consumer-facing applications.
            </li>
            <li>
              Learned Domain-Driven Design and Clean Architecture to navigate complex hardware/software domain, building
              bounded contexts that kept integrations modular and testable.
            </li>
            <li>
              Contributed hands-on to the user-facing ecosystem, building out web UIs using <strong>React</strong> and
              native mobile applications via Capacitor/Cordova.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="job-block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap gap-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl print:text-lg font-bold">Software Developer</h3>
            <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 whitespace-nowrap">April 2016 - July 2019</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-lg print:text-base italic text-gray-700 mb-2 print:mb-1">Visible Health</div>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
            <li>
              Primary contributor to <strong>DrawMD</strong>, an iPad application empowering doctors to visually explain
              surgical procedures and conditions to patients directly at the point of care.
            </li>
            <li>
              Navigated compliance and privacy restrictions of healthcare IT and HIPAA regulations.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="job-block space-y-2 print:space-y-1 pt-2 print:pt-0">
          <h3 class="text-xl print:text-lg font-bold">Earlier Experience</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-outside ml-5 space-y-1 text-gray-800">
            <li><strong>Software Developer</strong> at Escalation Point <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(Nov 2012 -
                Apr 2016)</span></li>
            <li><strong>Assistant Technical Director</strong> at Watershed 5 <span class="text-gray-600 text-sm">(Nov
                2008 - Nov 2012)</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-gray-300 print:my-2">

    <section class="space-y-2 print:space-y-1">
      <h2 class="text-2xl print:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">Education</h2>
      <div class="flex justify-between items-baseline flex-wrap gap-2">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg print:text-base font-bold">BFA, New Media: Design and Imaging</h3>
          <div class="italic text-gray-700">Rochester Institute of Technology</div>
        </div>
        <span class="font-medium text-gray-600 whitespace-nowrap">2004 - 2008</span>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</RootLayout>
